These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: corn, peach, raspberry
1. the person eating peach is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person eating raspberry and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Food   | peach     | corn    | raspberry   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, white, blood-red
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is between the person who likes emerald and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Color     | white | blood-red | emerald         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia, bellflower
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person who growsdahlia and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Flower        | dahlia  | bellflower | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, fanta
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person drinking tea is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | fanta     | tea |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Sport     | cycling    | surfing | biathlon    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, engineer, bartender
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the bartender and the videographer##2
2. the videographer is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Job   | videographer  | engineer   | bartender        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, superhero
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, dutch
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the brazilian is between the person watching superhero movies and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre          | time-travel  | scientific  | superhero |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian | dutch     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, september
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | september   | november  | december  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, american, chinese
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the american##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the chinese and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Nationality       | chinese | spanish | american  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

