.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
There 3 different types of food: onion, watermelon, corn
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person eating watermelon is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Food         | corn | watermelon | onion |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, blood-red, black
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person who likes blood-red and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person who likes black is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Color   | blood-red | apricot      | black      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

