The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dancer, doctor
1. the dancer is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the coach is between the owner of the mouse and the doctor##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Pet   | mouse  | bird   | goldfish  |
| Job        | dancer | coach | doctor |

