1. the person who likes mauve is between the mexican and the polish##2
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian   | polish   |
| Color         | orange  | mauve | ivory |

