.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, american, egyptian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the japanese is on the right of the american##1
2. the american is between the egyptian and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Nationality      | egyptian | american   | japanese |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 